ef.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.intel.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fwww%2Fpublic%2Fus%2Fen%2Fdocuments%2Fproduct-briefs%2Fxmm-7660-brief.pdf&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=e54b605a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.intel.com/content/dam/www/public/us/en/documents/product-briefs/xmm-7660-brief.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\ni don't see wifi<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30291701d104948482ca1a45352be70690b9ec85","tid":1865894,"uid":255744,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9c8335098e269ac47898d7a223a0b252a98d5f2","tid":1865894,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0456f2073dd164fb29879d183c714753029b88c","tid":1865894,"uid":255744,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"3241e674b2bad1ea843759d6ce2afddc30a01718","tid":1865894,"uid":241504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"4g先會用modem<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:30:33.000Z","msg":"手機粒modem三大負責項目<br />\n1 流動網絡<br />\n2 WiFi<br />\n3 藍牙"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.intel.com/content/dam/www/public/us/en/documents/product-briefs/xmm-7660-brief.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.intel.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fwww%2Fpublic%2Fus%2Fen%2Fdocuments%2Fproduct-briefs%2Fxmm-7660-brief.pdf&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=e54b605a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.intel.com/content/dam/www/public/us/en/documents/product-briefs/xmm-7660-brief.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\ni don't see wifi<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:44:07.000Z","msg":"intel咁求其，講粒modem得兩頁講咁少野？<br />\n<br />\n不如你睇吓以下<br />\n<br />\n「提到modem「貓」相信一些人肯定不會陌生，以前咱們上網都要用到它。從56K撥號上網到後來的ADSL寬頻上網，再到如今俗稱「光貓」技術誕生，「貓」進化史見證了這幾十年來智能生活的巨大演變。當初56K撥號上網時代電話線和上網線還是共用同一條傳輸信道的，所以每次打電話時候就會斷網，每次上網時候就會掛斷電話，而ADSL寬頻上網加入了分線器，讓上網和打電話兩不誤，傳輸速度和網絡帶寬也逐步提升，直到如今採用光纖電纜進行傳輸的光貓技術。<br />\n手機中也有這樣的「貓」，它放在我們常說的基帶晶片中，儘管其體積小，但它的作用卻比我們想像的更為重要，手機跟外界的一切連接性都跟這隻貓有關。比如，我們打電話，上網速度，LTE、WiFi連接等都需要它；全網通、雙卡雙待、更低功耗藍牙4.1等技術實現也全依賴它。下面我們就以市場上最主流，使用最廣泛的Qualcomm驍龍modem為例好好談一下手機中的數據機。」"},{"pid":"a615abb74da1a63d02f44b4d0a4395c71504bd52","tid":1865894,"uid":255744,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9c8335098e269ac47898d7a223a0b252a98d5f2","tid":1865894,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0456f2073dd164fb29879d183c714753029b88c","tid":1865894,"uid":255744,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"3241e674b2bad1ea843759d6ce2afddc30a01718","tid":1865894,"uid":241504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"4g先會用modem<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:30:33.000Z","msg":"手機粒modem三大負責項目<br />\n1 流動網絡<br />\n2 WiFi<br />\n3 藍牙"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.intel.com/content/dam/www/public/us/en/documents/product-briefs/xmm-7660-brief.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.intel.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fwww%2Fpublic%2Fus%2Fen%2Fdocuments%2Fproduct-briefs%2Fxmm-7660-brief.pdf&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=e54b605a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.intel.com